**LIX Calculator:** https://lexin.nada.kth.se/lix.html

**Steps to compute LIX score:**

1. Count the number of words in the text: 87
2. Count the number of sentences in the text: 13
3. Count the number of long words (words with more than 6 letters): 71

**LIX formula:** LIX = (words / sentences) + (long words / words) * 100

**Calculation:**

(87 / 13) + (71 / 87) * 100 = 6.74 + 81.61 = 88.35

**Result:**

LIX = 88.35